module.name: chained
module.description: Completes complex tasks using an automated loop

embeddings.text: Schedule a meeting, and don't forget to send invites to the attendees.
Send an email, including a file that you recently worked on.
Set an alarm that will wake you up with your favorite song playing.
Order a pizza, and let me know when it will be delivered.
Book a flight and reserve a hotel room for the same dates and location.
Find a nearby restaurant and book a table for two people at 7 PM.
Check the weather and suggest what to wear based on the forecast.
Play music from a specific genre and make sure the playlist is shuffled.
Find a product online, compare prices from different sellers, and let me know which one is the best
Set a timer for 30 minutes, and remind me to take a break and stretch my legs.
Translate a paragraph from English to Spanish or vice versa, and read it back to me.
Create a shopping list, and add items from a particular category, such as groceries or household supplies.
Find a recipe for a specific dish, and create a shopping list for the required ingredients.
Search for a specific article on a news website, and have it read aloud to me.
Call a specific contact, and put them on speakerphone so that I can continue with my work.
Set a reminder to water the plants every other day, and adjust the frequency based on the season and the plant's needs.
Calculate the tip amount for a specific bill, and split it among a group of people who are sharing the cost.
Convert a file from one format to another, and save it in a specific folder where it belongs.
Search for a specific video on a streaming platform, and add it to my watchlist for later.
